  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">&quot;for support of the Flexible Learning for Open Education program&quot;</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">&quot;The Inclusive Design Research Centre at the Ontario College of Art &amp; Design supports emerging, innovative design in digital systems with a special focus on inclusive education and OER. The Centre will further develop its Flexible Learning for Open Education program to address the needs of diverse learners by removing accessibility-related barriers to OER adoption, and it will continue to support deeper learning by encouraging students to discover, identify, and refine their understanding of how they learn best. This work advances the development and improvement of the technical infrastructure for the OER movement, especially as it relates to accessibility. &quot;</narrative>
  </description>
